  {
    "id": "noscope-cg8.5",
    "title": "Consolidate provider config and capability parsing",
    "description": "Reduce duplication and drift risk in provider configuration by unifying config model ownership and parsing paths.\\n\\nCurrent pain points:\\n- Parallel config structs for flags/env/file with overlapping fields\\n- Capability parsing logic separated from provider config parsing\\n- Repeated path-resolution patterns across modules\\n\\nAcceptance:\\n- Single authoritative provider config domain model\\n- Capability declarations validated in one owned parsing flow\\n- Clear precedence + validation pipeline with typed intermediate states",
    "status": "in_progress",
    "priority": 1,
    "issue_type": "feature",
